"title": "5559: stress",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5559",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of personal anxiety, strain or tension resulting from the pressures of human life. Scripture indicates a number of causes and means of dealing with stress.</p>\n<h2>The experience of stress</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:8\">PSA 38:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:33-Mark14:39\">MRK 14:33–14:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:37-Matt26:44\">MAT 26:37–26:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:39-Luke22:46\">LUK 22:39–22:46</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8\">2CO 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:2\">JOB 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:2\">PSA 77:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:19\">JER 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21\">JHN 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7\">HEB 5:7</a></p>\n<h2>Possible causes of stress</h2>\n<h3>Disobedience to God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65\">DEU 28:65</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:14\">2SA 24:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:13\">1CH 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:4\">PSA 38:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:9\">MAT 14:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:26\">MRK 6:26</a></p>\n<h3>Family ties</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:33\">1CO 7:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:11\">GEN 21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:6\">GEN 43:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:6-1Sam1:16\">1SA 1:6–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>The burdens of leadership</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:28\">2CO 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:14\">NUM 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></p>\n<h3>Threats of injury or violence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:20\">LAM 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:7\">GEN 32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:5\">1SA 28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:2\">1KI 19:1–19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:4\">EST 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:1-Ps56:2\">PSA 56:1–56:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:9\">JER 19:9</a></p>\n<h3>Unjust leaders</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:19\">EXO 5:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:37\">NEH 9:37</a></p>\n<h3>The wickedness of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:2-Rom9:3\">ROM 9:2–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:7-2Pet2:8\">2PE 2:7–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Academic study</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:13\">ECC 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>The effects of stress</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:18\">MRK 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:10\">PSA 31:9–31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:40-Luke10:41\">LUK 10:40–10:41</a></p>\n<h2>Appeals to God in stressful situations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:2\">PSA 102:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:2\">JON 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:7\">2SA 22:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:6\">PSA 18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:9\">2CH 20:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:12\">2CH 33:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:1\">PSA 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:17\">PSA 25:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:44\">PSA 106:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps120:1\">PSA 120:1</a></p>\n<h2>God comforts believers under stress</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:19\">PSA 94:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28\">MAT 11:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:7\">1PE 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:6\">1SA 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:6\">PSA 107:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:143\">PSA 119:143</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:8-2Cor4:10\">2CO 4:8–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a></p>",
